<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd">
<html><head><meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /><style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style></head><body style=" font-family:'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size:9.216pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">pipx</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 是一个 Python 工具，用于安装和管理 Python 应用程序的独立环境。与传统的 </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">pip</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 工具不同，</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">pipx</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 使得每个应用程序在一个单独的虚拟环境中运行，从而避免了依赖冲突和污染全局 Python 环境的问题。</span></p>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">主要特点</span></h3>
<ol style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">隔离环境</span>： 每个通过 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">pipx</span> 安装的应用程序都在自己的虚拟环境中运行，确保它们之间不会相互影响。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">便捷的命令行工具</span>： <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">pipx</span> 允许用户通过简洁的命令行界面轻松安装、更新和卸载应用程序。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">支持 Python 可执行包</span>： <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">pipx</span> 主要用于安装 Python 可执行包（即命令行工具），如 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">black</span>、<span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">flake8</span>、<span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">httpie</span> 等。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">自动处理依赖</span>： 在安装应用程序时，<span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">pipx</span> 会自动处理这些应用程序所需的所有依赖，确保它们能够正常工作。</li></ol>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">安装</span><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;">pipx</span></h3>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">你可以通过以下命令来安装</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">pipx</span><span style=" color:#000000;">：</span></p>
<pre style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#333333;">BASH</span><span style=" font-size:11pt; color:#ffffff; background-color:#007bff;">操作▼</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">python3 -m pip install --user pipx</span></pre>
<pre style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">python3 -m pipx ensurepath</span></pre>
<pre style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></pre>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">常用命令</span></h3>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">安装应用程序</span>：</li>
<pre style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#333333;">BASH</span><span style=" font-size:11pt; color:#ffffff; background-color:#007bff;">操作▼</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">pipx install </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;">&lt;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:696; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">package_name</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;">&gt;</span></pre>
<pre style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></pre>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">更新应用程序</span>：</li>
<pre style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#333333;">BASH</span><span style=" font-size:11pt; color:#ffffff; background-color:#007bff;">操作▼</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">pipx upgrade </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;">&lt;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:696; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">package_name</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;">&gt;</span></pre>
<pre style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></pre>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">卸载应用程序</span>：</li>
<pre style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#333333;">BASH</span><span style=" font-size:11pt; color:#ffffff; background-color:#007bff;">操作▼</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">pipx uninstall </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;">&lt;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:696; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">package_name</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;">&gt;</span></pre>
<pre style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:rgba(68,68,68,0.666667); background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></pre>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">列出已安装的应用程序</span>：</li></ul>
<pre style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#333333;">BASH</span><span style=" font-size:11pt; color:#ffffff; background-color:#007bff;">操作▼</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">pipx list</span></pre>
<pre style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></pre>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">示例</span></h3>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">假设你想安装</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">httpie</span><span style=" color:#000000;">，可以使用以下命令：</span></p>
<pre style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#333333;">BASH</span><span style=" font-size:11pt; color:#ffffff; background-color:#007bff;">操作▼</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">pipx install httpie</span></pre>
<pre style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></pre>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">安装完成后，你可以在命令行中直接使用</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">http</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 命令。</span></p>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">小结</span></h3>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">pipx</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 是一个非常实用的工具，适用于那些频繁使用 Python 命令行工具的开发者。它提供了简单的命令来管理 Python 应用程序的安装和运行，同时保持环境之间的隔离，使得依赖管理更加清晰和安全。</span></p></body></html>